<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
  <title>JS Bin</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="app" v-cloak>
    <h1>Hello, {{name}}</h1>
    <h2>{{Date()}}</h2>
    <img v-bind:src="smile ? feelsgood : feelsbad"/>
  </div>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/vue/dist/vue.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


JS
var app = new Vue({
  el: '#app', // 어떤 엘리먼트에 적용시킬것인지
  // data -> 해당 뷰에서의 사용할 정보를 지님
  data : {
    name: 'Vue',
    smile: true,
    feelsgood: 'https://image.ajunews.com/content/image/2019/05/24/20190524064406871980.png',
    feelsbad: 'data:image/jpeg;base64,'
  }
})
